WEBVTT

00:03.628 --> 00:06.339
<i>Previously on Your Honor...</i>

00:06.339 --> 00:09.926
<i>So your miraculous escape,
not so miraculous after all.</i>

00:09.926 --> 00:13.013
<i>And then Little Mo hides you
out in Houston with my sister,</i>

00:13.013 --> 00:14.472
<i>of all people, 'cause he knew</i>

00:14.472 --> 00:16.016
<i>I wouldn't go there
looking for you.</i>

00:16.016 --> 00:17.976
<i>You should have never
came back, Little Man.</i>

00:17.976 --> 00:20.020
<i>She was gonna kill you
if you took the money.</i>

00:20.020 --> 00:21.730
<i>You're lucky you're blood.</i>

00:21.730 --> 00:23.648
<i>You ain't fam.</i>

00:23.648 --> 00:25.358
<i>Not to me.</i>

00:25.358 --> 00:27.402
<i>Not no more.</i>

00:28.361 --> 00:30.030
<i>There's nothing
for me here anymore.</i>

00:30.030 --> 00:33.867
<i>Tomorrow, your ass is
on a bus back to H-Town.</i>

00:33.867 --> 00:35.368
<i>Fentanyl cut with heroin.</i>

00:35.368 --> 00:36.703
<i>You tried that shit?</i>

00:36.703 --> 00:38.371
<i>It's gonna be
the hottest shit in NOLA.</i>

00:38.371 --> 00:40.206
<i>You're my guinea pig, Joey.</i>

00:40.206 --> 00:43.001
<i>We were just talking about
the waterfront deal.</i>

00:43.001 --> 00:45.003
If this mayor is a problem,

00:45.003 --> 00:46.880
<i>there are ways to get a new one.</i>

00:46.880 --> 00:49.507
<i>I'm concerned
for Charlie's safety.</i>

00:49.507 --> 00:51.426
<i>If I can't do this deal
the way I wanted to,</i>

00:51.426 --> 00:53.053
<i>then other people are
gonna get involved.</i>

00:53.053 --> 00:56.556
<i>I am part of
a federal investigation</i>

00:56.556 --> 00:58.808
<i>into the Baxter organization.</i>

00:58.808 --> 01:00.894
<i>And you're just letting me in
on this now?</i>

01:00.894 --> 01:02.353
<i>I was trying to protect you.</i>

01:02.353 --> 01:04.022
<i>I can't make this deal.</i>

01:04.022 --> 01:05.732
<i>Not without some changes.</i>

01:05.732 --> 01:08.318
<i>The deal is done.
- What if she fails?</i>

01:08.318 --> 01:10.153
<i>She'll either bring down
the Baxters</i>

01:10.153 --> 01:12.405
<i>or the Baxters will build up
the waterfront.</i>

01:12.405 --> 01:15.867
<i>I need you to bury
his confession.</i>

01:15.867 --> 01:17.410
<i>What the hell's the point
of solving crimes</i>

01:17.410 --> 01:18.828
<i>if we're just gonna let
the criminals walk free?</i>

01:18.828 --> 01:21.247
<i>You may be free now...</i>

01:21.247 --> 01:22.874
<i>but that's not gonna
last forever.</i>

01:22.874 --> 01:24.918
<i>And when your
guardian angel vanishes,</i>

01:24.918 --> 01:28.088
<i>I'm gonna be
the next thing you see.</i>

01:30.507 --> 01:32.092
<i>Where were you...</i>

01:32.092 --> 01:34.636
<i>on the night of
your wife's murder?</i>

01:34.636 --> 01:37.639
<i>tense, suspenseful music</i>

01:55.698 --> 01:59.119
<i>October 10, the morning
after your wife was murdered,</i>

01:59.119 --> 02:01.579
<i>you gave this statement
to the NOPD.</i>

02:14.259 --> 02:16.970
<i>"I came home after work,
around seven o'clock.</i>

02:16.970 --> 02:18.638
<i>We had dinner together
as a family.</i>

02:18.638 --> 02:21.141
<i>Robin left around 9:00 or 9:30.</i>

02:21.141 --> 02:23.977
<i>Adam and I were home all night."</i>

02:27.772 --> 02:30.108
<i>Why are you asking me
about this now?</i>

02:30.108 --> 02:32.152
<i>She cheated on you.</i>

02:33.278 --> 02:34.988
<i>That must have stung.</i>

02:34.988 --> 02:37.699
<i>We never really
cleared that up, did we?</i>

02:38.324 --> 02:42.954
<i>I find it strange, your
reluctance to be forthcoming.</i>

02:53.214 --> 02:55.300
<i>This is you.</i>

02:55.300 --> 02:58.344
<i>This is the man
Robin had an affair with.</i>

02:58.344 --> 02:59.888
<i>This is the night
she was murdered.</i>

03:01.055 --> 03:03.224
<i>You look pretty mad, Michael.</i>

03:04.225 --> 03:05.727
<i>You haven't booked me.</i>

03:07.645 --> 03:09.439
<i>Because you don't have enough,</i>

03:09.439 --> 03:13.067
<i>if any, evidence to charge me.</i>

03:14.068 --> 03:16.487
<i>And yet, you have the audacity</i>

03:16.487 --> 03:19.699
<i>to march me through
the station in handcuffs?</i>

03:20.700 --> 03:22.619
<i>Oops.
- Mm.</i>

03:22.619 --> 03:24.204
<i>You're a person
of interest, though.</i>

03:24.204 --> 03:26.206
<i>I find you interesting.</i>

03:26.206 --> 03:28.875
<i>You know what's interesting?</i>

03:28.875 --> 03:30.543
<i>It only took you two years</i>

03:30.543 --> 03:32.378
<i>to come up with
the jealous husband theory?</i>

03:32.378 --> 03:37.300
<i>My opinion of you has evolved
quite a bit since then.</i>

03:37.300 --> 03:41.054
<i>So, now you think I'm capable
of killing my wife?</i>

03:41.054 --> 03:44.474
<i>I have no idea
what you're capable of anymore.</i>

03:45.558 --> 03:49.062
<i>The only question
that I'm interested in...</i>

03:49.062 --> 03:51.064
<i>is did you kill her?</i>

03:51.064 --> 03:54.234
<i>slow, dramatic music</i>

04:20.635 --> 04:23.680
Fuck you.

04:23.680 --> 04:25.807
Goddamn it.

04:26.975 --> 04:28.935
<i>What trouble
have you gotten into now?</i>

04:29.519 --> 04:33.898
<i>I just picked your ass up
at a police station, Michael.</i>

04:33.898 --> 04:35.608
<i>I want some answers.</i>

04:35.608 --> 04:38.611
<i>I was brought in for suspicion
of killing Robin Desiato.</i>

04:40.738 --> 04:42.865
<i>Yeah, I played that one
through in my mind, too.</i>

04:42.865 --> 04:44.158
<i>Many times.</i>

04:45.994 --> 04:47.745
<i>And what was your conclusion?</i>

04:47.745 --> 04:50.456
<i>For a while,
I actually wanted it to be you.</i>

04:51.666 --> 04:53.084
<i>But you couldn't have
killed my daughter.</i>

04:53.084 --> 04:54.961
<i>It's just not who you are.</i>

04:56.546 --> 04:59.048
<i>It's been two years.
Why do they suspect you now?</i>

05:02.010 --> 05:05.972
<i>They found out that I wasn't
home the night she was killed.</i>

05:05.972 --> 05:08.641
<i>I went to confront the man
she was sleeping with.</i>

05:08.641 --> 05:09.976
<i>You knew who he was?</i>

05:10.977 --> 05:12.603
<i>I did.</i>

05:12.603 --> 05:15.732
<i>And he's come forward now?</i>

05:15.732 --> 05:16.941
<i>Yeah.</i>

05:16.941 --> 05:18.776
<i>Well...</i>

05:18.776 --> 05:21.612
<i>I guess we're gonna go
talk to him then.</i>

05:21.612 --> 05:24.615
<i>slow, intriguing music</i>

05:42.050 --> 05:44.093
<i>Little Mo's gone.</i>

05:45.887 --> 05:47.764
<i>Time for y'all to step
your shit up.</i>

05:49.223 --> 05:51.601
<i>Once we're free and clear
of that Roderick motherfucker,</i>

05:51.601 --> 05:54.062
<i>we'll have good product to move.</i>

05:55.396 --> 05:58.316
<i>But until then,
we gotta deal with this shit.</i>

05:59.275 --> 06:00.526
<i>Come on.</i>

06:08.159 --> 06:10.912
<i>This is 30 milligrams of heroin.</i>

06:11.954 --> 06:13.706
<i>Enough to kill a grown man.</i>

06:13.706 --> 06:16.876
<i>But only three milligrams of
fentanyl will do the same thing.</i>

06:18.461 --> 06:20.004
<i>Now, all this shit is
cut with fenty,</i>

06:20.004 --> 06:21.714
<i>and not by
no motherfuckin' chemist.</i>

06:21.714 --> 06:25.593
<i>Which means the wrong baggie,
the wrong hit, you done.</i>

06:25.593 --> 06:27.053
<i>We just got to figure out
a way to move this</i>

06:27.053 --> 06:28.679
<i>without dropping bodies.</i>

06:28.679 --> 06:30.014
<i>Shit, every bag is
Russian roulette.</i>

06:30.014 --> 06:31.724
That's the problem.

06:31.724 --> 06:34.227
<i>I need a solution.
- Cut that shit again.</i>

06:34.227 --> 06:37.730
<i>Baking soda,
powdered milk, whatever.</i>

06:37.730 --> 06:39.732
<i>The high will be
weak as fuck, but...</i>

06:39.732 --> 06:41.401
<i>probably won't kill
nobody either.</i>

06:41.401 --> 06:42.902
<i>You did right
to pull it the first time.</i>

06:42.902 --> 06:45.071
<i>Bodies dropping is bad
for the neighborhood.</i>

06:45.071 --> 06:46.656
<i>That's why we're not
gonna sell it here.</i>

06:46.656 --> 06:49.242
<i>We send the corner boys
into the city.</i>

06:49.242 --> 06:50.993
<i>Spread it out.</i>

06:50.993 --> 06:54.872
<i>That way if anybody drops,
no one knows it's from here.</i>

06:54.872 --> 06:56.582
<i>And you cut
the motherfucker so thin</i>

06:56.582 --> 06:58.584
<i>that no bodies will drop.</i>

06:58.584 --> 06:59.919
<i>I got you.</i>

07:03.881 --> 07:06.259
<i>Top of the morning, Little Man.</i>

07:10.513 --> 07:12.765
<i>You make sure his ass
on that bus tonight.</i>

07:12.765 --> 07:15.768
<i>ominous music</i>

07:25.486 --> 07:30.408
<i>The mayor's stipulations
are going to be costly.</i>

07:30.408 --> 07:32.326
<i>So just in case,</i>

07:32.326 --> 07:36.706
<i>I got us a meeting with
some potential investors.</i>

07:36.706 --> 07:40.418
<i>Uh-huh?
What investors?</i>

07:40.418 --> 07:42.378
Old friends.

07:43.754 --> 07:47.300
<i>The Calabri Family
is interested.</i>

07:48.676 --> 07:49.927
<i>In what?</i>

07:49.927 --> 07:51.554
<i>A partnership.</i>

07:51.554 --> 07:53.639
<i>I don't want a partner.</i>

07:53.639 --> 07:55.641
<i>You want money, don't you?</i>

07:55.641 --> 07:58.811
<i>Come on, take the meeting.</i>

07:58.811 --> 08:00.646
<i>Let's hear their offer.</i>

08:01.606 --> 08:05.109
<i>contemplative music</i>

08:22.168 --> 08:24.170
<i>This is it?</i>

08:24.170 --> 08:25.671
<i>Yeah.</i>

08:35.306 --> 08:38.017
<i>Stay here if you want.
I'm gonna go get some answers.</i>

08:44.232 --> 08:45.858
<i>Kenneth.</i>

08:47.902 --> 08:49.445
<i>Michael.</i>

08:51.739 --> 08:54.367
<i>Elizabeth, by the way.</i>

08:54.367 --> 08:56.077
<i>I'm Robin's mother.</i>

09:20.768 --> 09:22.728
<i>Robin took this.</i>

09:23.646 --> 09:25.898
It was my favorite of hers.

09:28.276 --> 09:31.237
<i>I always thought her photos
elevated your articles.</i>

09:33.197 --> 09:35.116
<i>I agree with that.</i>

09:36.659 --> 09:38.327
<i>So, what do you want?</i>

09:38.327 --> 09:41.622
Why did you come forward now?

09:41.622 --> 09:43.374
Police came to me.

09:43.374 --> 09:44.875
<i>A couple days ago, they arrested</i>

09:44.875 --> 09:46.919
<i>some guy on grand theft auto.</i>

09:46.919 --> 09:49.714
<i>He wanted to exchange
information for a deal.</i>

09:49.714 --> 09:51.591
Who is he?

09:51.591 --> 09:55.177
<i>Former gang member who I used
as a source from time to time.</i>

09:55.177 --> 09:58.014
<i>Anyway, since I never
told the police</i>

09:58.014 --> 10:01.058
<i>about our relationship
and I gather you hadn't either,</i>

10:01.058 --> 10:03.269
<i>I guess this guy thought
they might want to know.</i>

10:03.269 --> 10:05.104
<i>Apparently, he was right</i>

10:05.104 --> 10:08.941
<i>'cause a Detective Costello
came to see me.</i>

10:08.941 --> 10:10.610
<i>And what did you tell her?</i>

10:10.610 --> 10:12.737
<i>That I was home all night.</i>

10:12.737 --> 10:15.281
<i>She asked me if anyone
could vouch for that.</i>

10:16.991 --> 10:18.909
<i>So I'm your alibi.</i>

10:18.909 --> 10:20.953
<i>And I'm yours.</i>

10:36.218 --> 10:39.180
<i>slow, dramatic music</i>

10:49.690 --> 10:51.484
<i>Can I...?</i>

10:51.484 --> 10:53.069
<i>Can I get a balloon?</i>

10:53.069 --> 10:54.779
<i>Man, we out.</i>

10:56.197 --> 10:57.490
<i>What do you mean you're out?</i>

10:57.490 --> 10:59.116
<i>Waiting on the drop.</i>

11:00.993 --> 11:03.245
<i>Come on, man, I got money.</i>

11:03.245 --> 11:04.997
<i>Get the fuck off me.</i>

11:07.249 --> 11:08.542
<i>This guy.</i>

11:17.051 --> 11:18.260
<i>Dad.</i>

11:18.260 --> 11:20.262
<i>Hey, Carlo.</i>

11:20.262 --> 11:22.014
<i>I've got a meeting right now.</i>

11:22.014 --> 11:24.016
<i>No, I know.
Uh, can I join?</i>

11:24.016 --> 11:25.851
<i>Better sit this one out.</i>

11:25.851 --> 11:28.145
<i>I won't say anything, Dad.
I just want to learn, you know?</i>

11:28.145 --> 11:29.855
<i>Next one, son.</i>

11:33.943 --> 11:37.071
<i>Gentlemen,
welcome to the Baxter House.</i>

11:37.071 --> 11:41.033
<i>Jimmy, this is Sal Calabri
and his son Phillip.</i>

11:41.033 --> 11:42.201
<i>Pleasure.</i>

11:42.201 --> 11:44.495
<i>My son-in-law Jimmy Baxter.</i>

11:44.495 --> 11:45.871
<i>Very nice to meet you.</i>

11:45.871 --> 11:48.207
<i>You, uh...
you flew in from New York?</i>

11:48.207 --> 11:49.542
<i>This morning.</i>

11:49.542 --> 11:51.502
<i>Why don't we all
have a seat, please?</i>

11:52.420 --> 11:54.672
<i>What can I do for you,
Mr. Calabri?</i>

11:54.672 --> 11:56.716
<i>We understand
that you're in need of</i>

11:56.716 --> 11:58.926
<i>a sizable infusion of capital.</i>

12:05.599 --> 12:08.686
<i>We are considering
taking on another investor.</i>

12:08.686 --> 12:09.895
We have an offer for you.

12:09.895 --> 12:12.189
<i>The eight figures that you need,</i>

12:12.189 --> 12:14.150
<i>same terms
you've given the others,</i>

12:14.150 --> 12:16.569
<i>with one additional item.</i>

12:16.569 --> 12:18.738
<i>We need access to your ports.</i>

12:19.905 --> 12:22.658
<i>Did I miss the news that
New York Harbor dried up?</i>

12:41.469 --> 12:43.304
<i>Jimmy, it's a good offer.</i>

12:46.140 --> 12:49.894
<i>How long would you want
to use... my ports?</i>

12:49.894 --> 12:51.103
Through the life of the loan.

12:51.103 --> 12:53.647
<i>After that, we can talk again.</i>

12:54.273 --> 12:59.403
<i>Anyone who knows me,
knows that I don't deal drugs.</i>

13:00.529 --> 13:04.325
<i>That's not the business
I want in my city.</i>

13:05.993 --> 13:09.455
<i>Nothing we bring in
stays in New Orleans.</i>

13:11.123 --> 13:12.625
Jimmy,

13:12.625 --> 13:15.795
<i>let's let these guys go
up to your rooms, relax,</i>

13:15.795 --> 13:17.797
<i>take a dip in the pool.</i>

13:17.797 --> 13:19.423
<i>We will meet up tonight.</i>

13:19.423 --> 13:22.718
<i>We'll eat, we'll drink,
we'll talk.</i>

13:24.136 --> 13:26.972
<i>tense, dramatic music</i>

13:35.147 --> 13:36.732
<i>When she told you
about our affair,</i>

13:36.732 --> 13:39.485
<i>I hoped that meant
she was ready to leave you.</i>

13:40.694 --> 13:41.987
<i>But she resisted.</i>

13:41.987 --> 13:43.823
<i>She and I had a fight
that night.</i>

13:43.823 --> 13:46.325
<i>And then she called you.
That's why I came here.</i>

13:46.325 --> 13:47.952
<i>She didn't call me that night.</i>

13:49.161 --> 13:50.996
<i>I heard her whispering
on the phone.</i>

13:50.996 --> 13:52.331
<i>It wasn't me.</i>

13:52.331 --> 13:54.208
Well, do you have any idea

13:54.208 --> 13:55.751
<i>who it might have been?</i>

14:00.714 --> 14:02.049
<i>I'm not out here in this swamp</i>

14:02.049 --> 14:03.551
<i>sweating through
my favorite blouse</i>

14:03.551 --> 14:06.679
<i>just to watch you refuse to
answer questions.</i>

14:09.223 --> 14:11.976
<i>There had been a string of hits.</i>

14:11.976 --> 14:15.813
<i>Upper-level members
of rival gangs.</i>

14:15.813 --> 14:17.773
<i>Eight in under a year.</i>

14:17.773 --> 14:19.692
<i>What's so intriguing
about a gang war?</i>

14:19.692 --> 14:23.362
<i>These weren't like gang hits.
They were clean.</i>

14:23.362 --> 14:25.698
<i>There was no brutality,</i>

14:25.698 --> 14:27.992
<i>there was no sending
of a message.</i>

14:27.992 --> 14:31.495
<i>It was just targeted executions.</i>

14:31.495 --> 14:33.831
<i>Never any witnesses.
Never any leads.</i>

14:33.831 --> 14:35.124
<i>All unsolved.</i>

14:35.124 --> 14:37.751
<i>So, what was
at the corner store?</i>

14:38.878 --> 14:40.129
<i>A witness.</i>

14:41.380 --> 14:43.007
<i>Tried to speak with him
days earlier,</i>

14:43.007 --> 14:45.050
<i>but he got spooked.</i>

14:45.050 --> 14:47.386
<i>He must have gotten
in contact with Robin.</i>

14:47.386 --> 14:49.388
<i>She was following up.
- What's his name?</i>

14:51.307 --> 14:53.517
<i>Please.</i>

14:53.517 --> 14:55.019
<i>KJ.</i>

14:57.980 --> 15:02.192
<i>He was gonna be the first to
confirm... our working theory.</i>

15:02.192 --> 15:04.069
<i>Which was what?</i>

15:05.321 --> 15:07.907
<i>It was cops doing
these killings.</i>

15:08.908 --> 15:11.577
<i>So, that's why
you hide out here?</i>

15:11.577 --> 15:13.537
<i>It's why I quit the story.</i>

15:13.537 --> 15:17.583
<i>And it's why I never revealed
any of this to the detectives.</i>

15:17.583 --> 15:21.337
<i>I couldn't trust who was clean
and who was dirty.</i>

15:21.337 --> 15:22.880
<i>Clearly, whoever was behind it</i>

15:22.880 --> 15:26.091
<i>wanted to make sure
the story died with us.</i>

15:26.091 --> 15:28.677
<i>I came out here because...</i>

15:28.677 --> 15:32.973
<i>I couldn't figure out how to
live my life with that pain.</i>

15:34.058 --> 15:37.019
<i>gentle, plaintive music</i>

15:39.939 --> 15:43.692
<i>She must have been so unhappy.</i>

15:46.654 --> 15:49.281
<i>I told her not to marry you.
- Jesus.</i>

15:51.075 --> 15:54.620
<i>I wasn't the worst husband
in the world.</i>

15:54.620 --> 15:56.830
<i>It wasn't you.
It was Robin.</i>

15:58.666 --> 16:02.127
<i>I was worried
she didn't love you enough.</i>

16:06.048 --> 16:08.008
<i>We had some good times.</i>

16:08.008 --> 16:10.260
<i>I know you did.</i>

16:10.260 --> 16:12.429
<i>Maybe I fought
too hard to keep her.</i>

16:12.429 --> 16:16.558
<i>I don't know, maybe
I should have just let her go.</i>

16:16.558 --> 16:18.769
<i>You couldn't have stopped her.</i>

16:18.769 --> 16:21.146
<i>It was Adam that kept her there.</i>

16:22.398 --> 16:24.942
<i>I have to know
what happened to my child.</i>

16:26.026 --> 16:29.822
<i>What if I told you
knowing doesn't help?</i>

16:29.822 --> 16:31.907
<i>I'd still want to know.</i>

16:40.040 --> 16:41.667
<i>What's wrong?
- Nothing.</i>

16:41.667 --> 16:43.419
<i>Carlo.</i>

16:43.419 --> 16:46.630
<i>Dad and Grandpa had a meeting,
and I wanted to join.</i>

16:46.630 --> 16:50.259
<i>And your father said no?</i>

16:50.259 --> 16:52.136
