<i>Playing out dozens of
scenarios in my head,</i>

34:20.224 --> 34:22.727
<i>not having a clue
what happened to her.</i>

34:22.727 --> 34:24.645
<i>I have to know.</i>

34:24.645 --> 34:26.731
<i>And I promise you,</i>

34:26.731 --> 34:30.443
<i>you will get no peace
until I do.</i>

34:36.574 --> 34:38.076
<i>Yeah, that's good.</i>

34:39.660 --> 34:41.746
<i>Hey, baby.</i>

34:41.746 --> 34:43.414
Hi.

34:43.414 --> 34:47.085
<i>Thank you so much
for letting us use this space.</i>

34:47.085 --> 34:48.961
<i>I bought that stage for you.</i>

34:53.091 --> 34:55.426
<i>Monique...</i>

34:55.426 --> 34:56.928
<i>What's wrong?</i>

34:57.553 --> 35:00.973
<i>Nothing for you to worry
your pretty face about.</i>

35:00.973 --> 35:03.518
<i>You want to talk about it?</i>

35:03.518 --> 35:05.978
<i>Don't ask, don't tell.
Remember?</i>

35:07.980 --> 35:09.482
<i>Mm.</i>

35:10.900 --> 35:13.653
<i>You have such a good heart.</i>

35:13.653 --> 35:15.905
<i>You don't have to
turn it off, you know?</i>

35:15.905 --> 35:18.574
<i>Only way to do the job.</i>

35:19.575 --> 35:21.619
<i>You do it long enough,</i>

35:21.619 --> 35:23.496
<i>you'll forget
how to turn it back on.</i>

35:27.667 --> 35:29.460
<i>How it feel?</i>

35:29.460 --> 35:31.295
<i>I'm with birds in a coupe,
what it do?</i>

35:31.295 --> 35:33.047
<i>I'm the motherfuckin' man,
who is you?</i>

35:33.047 --> 35:34.882
<i>Who is you?</i>

35:34.882 --> 35:36.884
<i>Just stick to the plan,
what's the move?</i>

35:36.884 --> 35:38.886
<i>What's the move?</i>

35:38.886 --> 35:41.305
<i>Know who I am, gotta choose,
got a bird's-eye...</i>

35:46.018 --> 35:47.645
<i>Who is you?</i>

35:47.645 --> 35:49.647
<i>Quit playin',
what's the move?</i>

35:49.647 --> 35:51.107
<i>What's the move?</i>

35:51.107 --> 35:53.151
<i>Know who I am, gotta choose</i>

35:53.151 --> 35:55.111
<i>Gotta choose,
really I been makin' moves</i>

35:55.111 --> 35:57.363
<i>Had to drop up out of school,
had to leave the job</i>

35:57.363 --> 35:59.157
<i>Had to find a muse</i>

35:59.157 --> 36:00.783
<i>Homie told me that
it's still in the shop</i>

36:00.783 --> 36:02.034
<i>Still see me carry twos</i>

36:02.034 --> 36:03.286
<i>Really he didn't feel me...</i>

36:50.708 --> 36:54.962
<i>You... stupid fuck.</i>

37:35.461 --> 37:38.422
<i>dramatic music</i>

38:29.265 --> 38:30.975
<i>Fuck you.</i>

38:32.059 --> 38:34.145
<i>You killed Kofi.</i>

38:37.023 --> 38:40.067
<i>You beat my brother to death
for no fucking reason.</i>

38:44.864 --> 38:47.575
<i>Then your daddy blew
my mama's house up.</i>

38:51.162 --> 38:53.247
<i>Killed my whole family.</i>

38:55.374 --> 38:58.002
<i>What did we ever do to you, huh?</i>

38:59.545 --> 39:01.672
<i>And after all of this...</i>

39:02.965 --> 39:06.344
<i>...you are trying to
fucking kill me?!</i>

39:12.099 --> 39:13.809
<i>So fuck me?</i>

39:17.521 --> 39:21.025
<i>Nah, man. Nah. Nah.</i>

39:22.610 --> 39:24.320
<i>Nah, fuck you.</i>

39:31.869 --> 39:33.829
<i>tense music</i>

40:08.864 --> 40:12.076
<i>A couple years back,
there was a turf war down here.</i>

40:12.076 --> 40:13.411
<i>It got real bad.</i>

40:13.411 --> 40:15.413
<i>Rival crews taking
each other out,</i>

40:15.413 --> 40:17.915
<i>but they couldn't get to
their top dogs.</i>

40:17.915 --> 40:19.417
<i>It was just
corner boys dropping.</i>

40:19.417 --> 40:20.960
<i>Then all of a sudden,</i>

40:20.960 --> 40:23.629
<i>a couple lieutenants get got,
on both sides.</i>

40:23.629 --> 40:25.256
<i>No one knows how,
no one knows who.</i>

40:25.256 --> 40:27.383
<i>It was police?</i>

40:27.383 --> 40:29.427
<i>That's why it never got solved.</i>

40:29.427 --> 40:31.303
<i>How do you know this?</i>

40:36.642 --> 40:40.104
<i>One of the cops used to
trade me drugs for information.</i>

40:40.104 --> 40:43.107
<i>Eventually,
I ran out of information,</i>

40:43.107 --> 40:46.152
<i>but he still had
the drugs, so...</i>

40:46.152 --> 40:49.530
<i>he made me pay for it
in other ways.</i>

40:52.575 --> 40:55.077
<i>You had a relationship
with this cop.</i>

41:00.499 --> 41:04.462
<i>It was a fucked-up situation,
but he trusted me.</i>

41:04.462 --> 41:07.798
<i>Or at least trusted
that he could control me.</i>

41:09.133 --> 41:10.426
<i>So he talked.</i>

41:10.426 --> 41:13.137
<i>Spilled his guts
like I was his priest.</i>

41:13.137 --> 41:15.139
<i>He'd tell me about the shit
he did on the job,</i>

41:15.139 --> 41:16.640
<i>like he was bragging.</i>

41:16.640 --> 41:18.434
<i>Stealing drugs, money...</i>

41:18.434 --> 41:20.269
<i>Planting things on folks
that pissed him off.</i>

41:28.360 --> 41:30.154
<i>Shit like that.</i>

41:31.739 --> 41:34.158
<i>Then one night,</i>

41:34.158 --> 41:36.869
<i>he tells me that
he just shot a guy.</i>

41:36.869 --> 41:40.539
<i>Execution style.
Murder for hire.</i>

41:40.539 --> 41:43.501
<i>Not long after that,
I told him I was done.</i>

41:43.501 --> 41:46.712
<i>I was trying to get clean.
Didn't want to see him anymore.</i>

41:46.712 --> 41:50.174
<i>I get a call
from this woman named Robin.</i>

41:50.174 --> 41:52.051
<i>She said she's
working on a story</i>

41:52.051 --> 41:55.054
<i>about police brutality,
and asked if I wanted to talk.</i>

41:55.054 --> 41:56.931
<i>I should have just kept
my fucking mouth shut,</i>

41:56.931 --> 41:58.849
<i>but I thought
my life was over anyway.</i>

41:58.849 --> 42:02.353
<i>I told her I knew that
cops were killing people</i>

42:02.353 --> 42:04.522
<i>and that I'd talk to her
when I got out.</i>

42:06.982 --> 42:08.817
<i>She must've realized
I was getting cold feet</i>

42:08.817 --> 42:11.862
<i>because one night I look up
and there she is.</i>

42:11.862 --> 42:13.322
<i>Wait.</i>

42:13.322 --> 42:16.158
<i>She didn't call you
the night she came here?</i>

42:16.158 --> 42:18.369
<i>Before she came here?
- No.</i>

42:18.369 --> 42:21.372
<i>Because I wouldn't have
been here if she did.</i>

42:21.372 --> 42:25.125
<i>She walked in
and he was right behind her.</i>

42:26.085 --> 42:27.670
<i>She barely makes it
to the register</i>

42:27.670 --> 42:30.381
<i>when he opened fire.</i>

42:30.381 --> 42:31.882
<i>She never saw it coming.</i>

42:35.886 --> 42:39.223
<i>So, you-you... you saw this?</i>

42:40.641 --> 42:43.602
<i>I saw a mask and gloves.</i>

42:43.602 --> 42:45.396
<i>But I knew it was him.</i>

42:45.396 --> 42:47.940
<i>You sure?
- I'm positive.</i>

42:47.940 --> 42:50.901
<i>KJ, tell us who he is.</i>

42:56.615 --> 42:58.325
<i>Please.</i>

42:59.827 --> 43:02.413
<i>We would never reveal your name.</i>

43:02.413 --> 43:04.248
<i>That's a promise.</i>

43:14.466 --> 43:17.094
<i>Detective Walter Beckwith.</i>

43:17.094 --> 43:19.597
Beckwith?

43:19.597 --> 43:22.600
<i>slow, dramatic music</i>

43:24.643 --> 43:26.103
<i>Thank you.</i>

43:27.229 --> 43:29.940
<i>Does it feel weird
seeking spiritual advice</i>

43:29.940 --> 43:31.734
<i>from someone
who's half your age?</i>

43:31.734 --> 43:33.944
<i>You need to check your math.</i>

43:38.616 --> 43:39.908
<i>Hi.</i>

43:39.908 --> 43:42.620
<i>Uh, I-I don't know what to do.</i>

43:42.620 --> 43:44.121
<i>He... he won't stop crying.</i>

43:44.121 --> 43:45.956
<i>Just give him to me.</i>

43:45.956 --> 43:48.000
<i>Where the hell is my brother?</i>

43:48.000 --> 43:49.501
<i>Um...
- Where is Carlo?!</i>

43:49.501 --> 43:51.337
<i>He left. He left.</i>

43:51.337 --> 43:52.880
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

43:54.798 --> 43:56.592
Hey, Detective.

43:56.592 --> 43:58.177
<i>What in the hell happened?</i>

43:58.177 --> 44:00.512
<i>Driver of the other car
was likely intoxicated.</i>

44:00.512 --> 44:03.390
<i>But this one's Desire.
That's why we called you.</i>

44:03.390 --> 44:04.808
Was anyone else with him?

44:04.808 --> 44:07.144
<i>He said he was alone.
- Mm.</i>

44:10.814 --> 44:12.316
<i>You all right?</i>

44:26.372 --> 44:27.998
<i>Anyone else in the car?</i>

44:27.998 --> 44:29.667
<i>Nah.</i>

44:43.889 --> 44:46.016
<i>suspenseful music</i>

45:08.914 --> 45:11.375
<i>I need to talk to him
for a minute.</i>

45:12.793 --> 45:14.753
Bus 232, service--

45:14.753 --> 45:16.714
<i>service to Baton Rouge, Lafayette,</i>

45:16.714 --> 45:19.383
<i>and points west,
is now ready to depart.</i>

45:19.383 --> 45:21.802
<i>All ticketed passengers
should be on board.</i>

45:21.802 --> 45:23.470
<i>Thank you.</i>

45:27.057 --> 45:29.184
<i>I'm gonna go lie down.</i>

45:29.184 --> 45:30.644
Okay.

45:34.106 --> 45:37.025
<i>You were right.
It doesn't help.</i>

45:37.025 --> 45:39.820
<i>She's dead. She shouldn't be.
I already knew that.</i>

45:41.238 --> 45:43.741
<i>I just... I just didn't
want her to think</i>

45:43.741 --> 45:46.243
<i>I didn't care enough
to ask the questions.</i>

45:52.124 --> 45:53.542
Elizabeth.

45:54.918 --> 45:58.714
<i>I should have been there for you
after she died.</i>

45:59.798 --> 46:01.925
<i>You were dealing with
your own loss.</i>

46:01.925 --> 46:04.136
<i>Yeah, but I...</i>

46:04.136 --> 46:06.555
<i>I had Adam.</i>

46:06.555 --> 46:08.766
<i>And I-I just...</i>

46:10.100 --> 46:13.270
<i>I just didn't appreciate that</i>

46:13.270 --> 46:16.607
<i>he was your connection to
the child you'd lost.</i>

46:19.318 --> 46:23.614
<i>There is nothing quite like
the wonder of a grandchild.</i>

46:27.326 --> 46:29.369
<i>No, there's not.</i>

46:31.455 --> 46:34.041
<i>Elizabeth, I-I...</i>

46:34.041 --> 46:38.128
<i>I was going to wait to tell you.</i>

46:38.128 --> 46:40.964
<i>I don't know when.</i>

46:40.964 --> 46:42.633
<i>But, uh...</i>

46:44.760 --> 46:47.262
<i>Fia Baxter...</i>

46:47.262 --> 46:49.014
<i>has a baby.</i>

46:50.349 --> 46:51.975
<i>A little boy.</i>

46:55.020 --> 46:57.022
<i>You are a great-grandmother.</i>

47:00.150 --> 47:02.277
<i>Adam's son?
- Yes.</i>

47:03.153 --> 47:05.864
<i>Have you met him?</i>

47:05.864 --> 47:08.325
<i>Mm.
- And?</i>

47:10.202 --> 47:11.370
<i>He's perfect.</i>

47:11.370 --> 47:13.330
<i>Oh.</i>

47:14.540 --> 47:16.083
<i>Come here.</i>

47:16.083 --> 47:18.001
Come here.

47:18.001 --> 47:19.503
<i>Come here.</i>

47:23.298 --> 47:25.717
<i>Right in here. 237.
- Oh, my God. There he is.</i>

47:25.717 --> 47:27.386
<i>Carlo.</i>

47:27.386 --> 47:28.887
<i>Carlo, you okay?</i>

47:28.887 --> 47:31.098
<i>Yeah, I'm fine, Mom.
- Oh, my God.</i>

47:31.098 --> 47:32.516
<i>What happened, son?</i>

47:32.516 --> 47:35.143
<i>What happened?
What happened?</i>

47:35.143 --> 47:37.020
<i>I was in a car accident
with Joey.</i>

47:37.020 --> 47:38.689
<i>Maldini?</i>

47:38.689 --> 47:40.482
<i>What were you doing
leaving Rocco?</i>

47:40.482 --> 47:42.943
<i>Carlo, how could you
leave my son</i>

47:42.943 --> 47:44.361
<i>with a fucking stranger?</i>

47:44.361 --> 47:45.863
<i>Fia, Fia.
- Can we talk about this later?</i>

47:45.863 --> 47:47.739
<i>No, I need an answer right now.</i>

47:48.866 --> 47:51.827
<i>Joey came to the hotel.</i>

47:51.827 --> 47:54.037
<i>He said he was
in the Lower Ninth earlier.</i>

47:54.037 --> 47:55.539
<i>And he saw Eugene Jones.</i>

47:59.209 --> 48:01.545
<i>I thought he was disposed of.
- So did I.</i>

48:01.545 --> 48:03.589
No, I saw him.

48:03.589 --> 48:06.049
<i>And I had the chance to
take the fucker out.</i>

48:06.049 --> 48:08.093
<i>So, did you?</i>

48:08.093 --> 48:10.220
<i>Did you "take the fucker out"?</i>

48:12.514 --> 48:14.224
<i>He tried to kill me.</i>

48:15.434 --> 48:17.895
<i>What is wrong with this family?</i>

48:17.895 --> 48:19.521
<i>I'm so fucking done</i>

48:19.521 --> 48:20.981
<i>with all of you.
-</i>

48:20.981 --> 48:22.691
<i>Fia.</i>

48:23.317 --> 48:26.403
<i>What happened to him?
What happened to the boy?</i>

48:26.403 --> 48:29.197
<i>I was trapped in the car.
He got away.</i>

48:30.449 --> 48:32.743
<i>Frankie, I want that boy found. Tonight.</i>

48:32.743 --> 48:33.785
<i>I'll handle this.</i>

48:33.785 --> 48:35.871
<i>You had your chance!</i>

48:44.087 --> 48:46.048
<i>I need a word.</i>

48:46.048 --> 48:47.341
<i>Not right now.</i>

48:59.478 --> 49:01.605
<i>Look at me, James.</i>

49:04.274 --> 49:07.986
<i>Are you so afraid of being
like that drunk daddy of yours,</i>

49:07.986 --> 49:10.072
<i>that you have forgotten</i>

49:10.072 --> 49:13.200
<i>what it takes to be a man, huh?</i>

49:13.200 --> 49:16.078
<i>Hmm? Nut the fuck up!</i>

49:34.513 --> 49:36.348
<i>Cusack has to call me back.</i>

49:36.348 --> 49:39.059
<i>Last I heard, Joey left town,
he was living on the streets.</i>

49:39.059 --> 49:42.145
<i>He should have been dead by now.
Our own cops even said so.</i>

49:43.355 --> 49:45.148
<i>I agree with Gina, Jim.</i>

49:45.148 --> 49:48.568
<i>Let's find Eugene and let's send
a message to the whole city.</i>

49:49.778 --> 49:52.280
Jimmy!

49:55.993 --> 49:57.494
<i>Jim, Jim, no--</i>

49:57.494 --> 49:58.829
<i>Jim...</i>

50:12.509 --> 50:14.469
<i>tense music</i>

50:25.689 --> 50:27.315
I'm good, I'm good.

50:31.570 --> 50:33.864
<i>What's up with y'all?</i>

50:43.623 --> 50:45.333
<i>Chris, the fuck is up?</i>

50:48.587 --> 50:50.047
<i>My little brother...</i>

50:52.466 --> 50:54.384
<i>He took one of the balloons.</i>

50:55.969 --> 50:57.262
<i>He dead.</i>

51:00.974 --> 51:03.560
<i>slow, somber music</i>

51:06.897 --> 51:08.565
<i>Chris...</i>

51:20.035 --> 51:21.244
<i>Costello.</i>

51:21.244 --> 51:23.205
Nancy, it's Michael.

51:23.205 --> 51:26.208
<i>I think I know why you weren't
able to solve Robin's murder.</i>

51:27.626 --> 51:29.628
<i>The killer was one of your own.</i>

51:29.628 --> 51:32.464
<i>tense music</i>

51:37.094 --> 51:39.054
<i>Can you come to the station?</i>

51:39.054 --> 51:41.348
<i>Yeah. On my way.</i>

51:54.820 --> 51:56.822
<i>Thank you.</i>

51:57.447 --> 51:59.991
Bus 58 going up to Houston

